        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="grc">
                    <ab>
                        <lb n="1"/><g ref="hedera"/> Πετρώνιον Πρόβον, <g ref="hedera"/>
                        <lb n="2"/>τὸν λαμπρότατον <g ref="hedera"/>
                        <lb n="3"/>ἀπὸ ὑπάτων καὶ <g ref="hedera"/>
                        <lb n="4"/>ἀπὸ ἐπάρχων πραιτωρίων
                        <lb n="5"/><g ref="hedera"/> γʹ, <g ref="hedera"/> δόγματι τῆς λαμπρᾶς
                        <lb n="6"/>Γορτυνίων βουλῆς,
                        <lb n="7"/>Οἰκουμένιος Δωσίθεος
                        <lb n="8"/>Ἀσκληπιόδοτος <g ref="hedera"/>
                        <lb n="9"/>ὁ λαμπρότατος ὑπατι<lb 
                            break="no" n="10"/>κὸς ἀνέστησεν. <g ref="hedera"/>
                    </ab>
            </div>
            <div type="apparatus">
                <p>Edition based on ICret.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" xml:lang="en">
                <p>“To Petronius Probus, of clarissimus rank, former consul and former praetorian prefect for the third time, according to the decree of the bright council of Gortyna, Oecumenius Dositheus Asclepiodotus, consular of clarissimus rank, set up.”</p>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" xml:lang="fr">
                <p>“...”</p>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" xml:lang="it">
                <p>“A Petronius Probus, chiarissimo ex console ed ex prefetto del pretorio per la terza volta, per decreto dello splendido consiglio di Gortina, Oecumenius Dositheus Asclepiodotus, clarissimo consolare, pose.”</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>...</p>
            </div>
